name: Ekphrasis XXIV
description: This is the age of algorithm. The normalized culture of constant distraction and toxic hyperconnectedness with our devices, knowing we are already being watched; we are already being played by Big Brother out there, seeing everything we Post, Like, Share, and knowing which marketing and advertising tactics will work on us, and which kind of political propaganda will confirm our biases and stoke our personal beliefs. The dark side of the internet that we refuse to talk about.
